### Row names

You can also convert a column into table rownames and specify it in the original `gt()` call.

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
head(mtcars) %>% 
  mutate(cyl = paste(cyl, "Cylinders")) %>% 
  gt(rowname_col = "cyl")
```

