#### Relabel with markdown or HTML

You can also parse markdown with `md()` or HTML with `html()` within the label string.

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
head(mtcars) %>% 
  gt() %>% 
  cols_label(
    mpg = md("**Miles/Gal**"),       # recognizes markdown syntax
    cyl = html("<em>Cylinders</em>") # recognizes HTML syntax
  )
```

