### Move columns

You can move columns to the beginning, end, or arbitrary locations.

#### To start

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
countrypops %>% 
  dplyr::select(country_name, year:population) %>% 
  tail(8) %>% 
  gt() %>% 
  cols_move_to_start(vars(year))
```

