### Merge columns

Columns can be merged with `glue`-like syntax.

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sp500 %>%
  dplyr::slice(50:55) %>%
  dplyr::select(-volume, -adj_close) %>%
  gt() %>%
  cols_merge(
    columns = vars(open, close),
    hide_columns = vars(close),
    pattern = "{1}&mdash;{2}"
  ) %>%
  cols_merge(
    columns = vars(low, high),
    hide_columns = vars(high),
    pattern = "{1}&mdash;{2}"
  ) %>%
  cols_label(
    open = "open/close",
    low = "low/high"
  )
```

